{"body": "with total_purchases as (
  select 
  account_id as account_id,
  sum(cast (actions.value as bignumeric)) as purchases
  from facebook_ads.unnested_insights
  where actions.action_type='omni_purchase' and type = 'actions'
	and parse_date('%Y-%m-%d', date_start) between '{{startDate.selectedDate}}' and '{{endDate.selectedDate}}'
  group by account_id
)

,total_purchase_value as (
  select 
  account_id as account_id, 
  sum(cast (actions.value as bignumeric)) as purchase_value
  from facebook_ads.unnested_insights
  where actions.action_type='omni_purchase' and type = 'action_values'
	and parse_date('%Y-%m-%d', date_start) between '{{startDate.selectedDate}}' and '{{endDate.selectedDate}}'
  group by account_id
)

,grouped_ads as (
	select 
tile_id,
ad_id,
sum(cast (spend as bignumeric)) as spend,
min(total_purchases.purchases) as purchases,
sum(cast (clicks as bignumeric)) as clicks,
sum(cast (impressions as bignumeric)) as impressions,
min(total_purchase_value.purchase_value) as purchase_value
from facebook_ads.ad_insights_per_tile as insights
left join total_purchases
on total_purchases.account_id = insights.ad_id
left join total_purchase_value
on total_purchase_value.account_id = insights.ad_id
where parse_date('%Y-%m-%d', date_start) between '{{startDate.selectedDate}}' and '{{endDate.selectedDate}}'
group by ad_id, tile_id
)

,tile_ad_performance as (
		select 	
	tile_id,
	count(*) as total_ads,
	sum(cast (spend as bignumeric)) as spend,
	sum(purchases) as purchases,
	sum(cast (impressions as bignumeric)) as impressions,
	sum(cast (clicks as bignumeric)) as clicks,
	round(safe_divide(sum(cast (clicks as bignumeric)), sum(cast (impressions as bignumeric))) * 100, 2) as ctr,
	round(safe_divide(sum(cast (spend as bignumeric)), sum(cast (impressions as bignumeric))) * 1000, 2) as cpm,
	round(safe_divide(sum(cast (clicks as bignumeric)), sum(cast (spend as bignumeric))), 2) as cpc,
	round(safe_divide(sum(purchase_value), sum(cast (spend as bignumeric))), 2) as roas,
	round(safe_divide(sum(cast (spend as bignumeric)), sum(purchases)), 2) as cost_per_purchase
	from grouped_ads
	group by tile_id
	order by spend desc
	)
	
,tile_performance as (
		select 
	tile_id,
	brand_id,
	min(tile_name) as tile_name,
	min(brand_name) as brand_name,
	min(tile_type) as tile_type,
	sum(total_checkout_count) as checkouts,
	sum(gmv) as gmv,
	round(safe_divide(sum(gmv), sum(total_checkout_count)), 2) as aov,
	round(safe_divide(sum(total_checkout_count), sum(total_impression_count)) * 100, 2) as cvr
	from checkouts.tile_conversion_stats
	where parse_date('%Y-%m-%d', string(date)) between '{{startDate.selectedDate}}' and '{{endDate.selectedDate}}'
	and if ({{selectedBrands.selectedOptionValues.length > 0}}, brand_id in unnest({{selectedBrands.selectedOptionValues}}), brand_id is not null)
	group by tile_id, brand_id
	)
	
	select * from 
	tile_performance 
	left join tile_ad_performance
	on tile_ad_performance.tile_id = tile_performance.tile_id
	where spend is not null or cvr != 0
	order by spend desc", "usePreparedSql": false, "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.7"}}

{"body": "-- You can use SQL to query data (ex. SELECT * FROM orders;)

select
   case
    when link like '%new-york%' then 'New York'
    when link like '%london%' then 'London'
    else ''
    end as EventName,
   cam.id as campaignId,
   cam.name,
   link,
   cam.send_amt,
   cam.uniqueopens,
   cls.uniquelinkclicks,
   cls.campaign,
   cam.sdate as campaignDate
from `durable-gift-291009.activecampaign_stitch_clone.campaign_links` cls
inner join `activecampaign_stitch_clone.campaigns` cam on cls.campaign = cam.id
where send_amt > 0 
order by cam.id desc", "usePreparedSql": true, "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.7"}}

{"body": "-- You can use SQL to query data (ex. SELECT * FROM orders;)

select
	njr.id, njr.status, njr.recipient_email, njr.message_id, njr.created_at, njr.details,
	case when ed.destination is not null then true else false end as delivered,
	(
			select count(*)
		from
	emails_opentable eo
		where njr.recipient_email = eo.destination
		and eo.campaign = {{tJobLog.selectedRow.campaign_name}}

	) as "Num Open",
	(
			select count(*)
		from
	emails_clicktable ec
		where njr.recipient_email = ec.destination
		and ec.campaign = {{tJobLog.selectedRow.campaign_name}}

	) as "Num Click"	
from
	notifications_job_record njr
	left join
	emails_deliverytable ed
		on njr.recipient_email = ed.destination and ed.campaign = {{tJobLog.selectedRow.campaign_name}}

where
	notification_job_log_id = {{tJobLog.selectedRow.id ?? 0}}", "operation": "run_sql", "usePreparedSql": true, "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.8"}}

{"body": "with five_min_intervals as (
  select 
    (select {{new Date(NextFriday.text).toISOString()}}::timestamp) - ( n    || ' weeks')::interval end_time,
    (select {{new Date(NextFriday.text).toISOString()}}::timestamp) - ((n+1) || ' weeks')::interval start_time
  from generate_series(0, 4) n
)
-- select (select max("time") from rep_accounts), * from five_min_intervals order by start_time desc
select f.start_time, f.end_time, m.submitter_email, count(m.id) c 
from rep_accounts m
right join five_min_intervals f 
        on m.time >= f.start_time and m.time < f.end_time
group by f.start_time, f.end_time, m.submitter_email
having m.submitter_email in ('brandon@superblockshq.com', 'jeff@superblockshq.com', 'ryan@superblockshq.com')
order by f.start_time desc", "usePreparedSql": true, "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.8"}}

{"body": "with tweets as ( select t.user.name, t.text, t.user.followers_count, t.user.friends_count, upper(sym.text) as ticker, t.id_str as TweetID, RTRIM(SUBSTR(t.source,STRPOS(t.source,'>')+1),'') as source, TIME_BUCKET(Minutes(1),t._event_time) as Tweet_Date from Demo.tweets_alias as t, unnest(t.entities.symbols) as sym where t.entities.symbols [1] is not null and t._event_time between timestamp'2023-03-08' and timestamp'2023-03-08' + HOURS(1) ) select tw.Tweet_Date, tw.name as Username, tw.TweetID, tw.ticker, tkr.Industry, tkr.Name, tw.followers_count, tw.friends_count, 1 as tweetCount, tw.source, tw.text from tweets as tw join Demo.tickers_alias as tkr on tkr.Symbol = tw.ticker order by 1;", "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.6"}}

{"body": "WITH
    p_pspcs as (
        SELECT
            p.tenantId as pc_tenantId,
            p.id as pc_platformId,
            pspc.*
        FROM
            prod."prod-platforms" p,
            unnest(p."pspConfigs") as pspc
        where
    p.tenantId IN ('{{selectTenants.selectedOptionValues.join("','")}}')
{{ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.length ? "and p.id IN ('"+ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.join("','")+"')" : "" }}
    ),
    p_evtcs as (
        SELECT
            ec.id as ec_id,
            ec.type as ec_type,
            ec.platformId as ec_tenantId,
            ec.platformId as ec_platformId,
            evtc.*
        FROM
            prod."prod-eventConfig" ec,
            unnest(ec."configs") as evtc
        where
    ec.tenantId IN ('{{selectTenants.selectedOptionValues.join("','")}}')
{{ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.length ? "and ec.platformId IN ('"+ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.join("','")+"')" : "" }}
    )
select
    pp.tenantId,
    pp.id as platformId,
    pp.parentId,
		pp.platforms,
    pp.name,
    pp.label,
    -- branding    
    pp.logoUrl,
    pp.supportEmail,
    -- ux
    pp.ux,
    pp.twoStepUx,
    pp.showCgu,
		-- services
		COALESCE(pp.pbl, false) as pbl,
		COALESCE(pp.subscription, false) as subscription,
		COALESCE(pp.invoice, false) as invoice,
		COALESCE(pp.quote, false) as quote,
		COALESCE(tn.reporting, false) as reporting,
		case 
			when (tn.groupService = true and tn.airline = true) then 'GS Airline'
			when (tn.groupService = true) then 'GS DMA'
			else false
		end as "Group Service",
    -- PMM
		pp.isModule,
		pp.modules,
    pp.moduleChoices,
    -- intl
    pp.locale,
    pp.currency,
    pp.allowedCurrencies,
    -- PAM
    pp.authMode,
    pp.completionMode,
    pp.confirmationNotif,
    pp.delay,
    pp.paylaterChoices,
    pp.installmentsCount,
    pp.installmentsChoices,
    -- webhooks
    pp.webhookVersion,
    pp.webhookSecretKey,
    pp.notifyUrl,
    -- processing
    pp.directCapture,
    pp.pspConfigs,
    p_pspcs.*,
    -- fees config
    pp.feesConfig,
    -- event configs
    p_evtcs.ec_id,
    p_evtcs.ec_type,
    p_evtcs.events as ec_events,
    p_evtcs.actions as ec_actions,
		pp.withdrawalConfig,
from
    prod."prod-platforms" pp
		join prod."prod-tenants" tn on tn.id = pp.tenantId
    left join p_evtcs on p_evtcs.ec_platformId = pp.id
    left join p_pspcs on p_pspcs.pc_platformId = pp.id
where
    pp.tenantId IN ('{{selectTenants.selectedOptionValues.join("','")}}')
{{ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.length ? "and pp.id IN ('"+ selectPlatforms.selectedOptionValues.join("','")+"')" : "" }}
		
    ", "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.6"}}

{"body": "SELECT
    '{{ValidateInput.output.day}}' as day,
    entityType,
    entityId,
    userId,
    organizationId,
    entityName,
		count(*) as creatorEventsCount,
		'{{ValidateInput.output.now}}' as updatedAt
FROM
    prod."user-events" u
WHERE
    u._event_time >= DATE '{{ValidateInput.output.day}}'
    and u._event_time < DATE '{{ValidateInput.output.day}}' + INTERVAL 1 DAY
    -- exclude application events
    and entityType != 'application'
		and u.properties.applicationId is null
    -- get creator events
    and type in {{CreatorEvents.output}}
    and u.organizationId != '70bb9df0-a95c-4c29-8a0b-669ba9bc00ab' -- superblocks test
		and u.email NOT like '%superblockshq.com'
group by
    day,
    entityType,
    entityId,
    userId,
    organizationId,
    entityName", "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.6"}}

{"body": "select
    p.name,
    p.label,
    o.id as orderId,
    o.amount / 100.00 o_amount,
    o.ux,
    o.status as o_status,
    o.createdAt as o_createdAt,
    FORMAT_DATE (
        '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S',
        DATETIME(TIMESTAMP_MILLIS(o."createdAt"), 'Europe/Paris')
    ) as o_createdAt_h,
		t.id as transactionId,
    t.amount / 100.00 as t_amount,
    t.status as t_status,
    t.createdAt as t_createdAt,
    FORMAT_DATE (
        '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S',
        DATETIME(TIMESTAMP_MILLIS(t."createdAt"), 'Europe/Paris')
    ) as t_createdAt_h,
		concat('https://d3p4082e4erx6h.cloudfront.net/orders/view/', o.id) as admin_link
from
    prod."prod-transactions" t
    join prod."prod-orders" o on o.id = t.orderId
    join prod."prod-platforms" p on o.platformId = p.id
where
    t.status = 'authorized'
    and o.status = 'completed'
		-- test on this and o.createdAt > 1669849200000
		and o.createdAt > 1678732063348
		and TIMESTAMP_MILLIS(o.updatedAt) <= (CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() - INTERVAL 10 MINUTE)   
order by t.updatedAt desc", "superblocksMetadata": {"pluginVersion": "0.0.6"}}

{"body": "SELECT
     '{{ValidateInput.output.day}}' as day,

    '{{ValidateInput.output.now}}' as updatedAt
